Instructions for repeating the experiments from Baker et al. "Cancer
Hallmark Text Classification Using Convolutional Neural Networks" (BioTxtM'16)

# Development experiments

## Base

    ./run-base-model.sh
    mv logs/ logs-base
    ./summarize-devel.sh logs-base/*

## Oversampling

    ./run-oversampled.sh
    mv logs logs-oversampled    
    ./summarize-devel.sh logs-oversampled/*

## Word vectors

    ./run-wordvecs.sh
    mv logs logs-wordvecs
    ./summarize-wordvecs.sh logs-wordvecs/*

## Filter sizes

    ./run-filters.sh
    mv logs logs-filtes
    ./summarize-filters.sh logs-filters/*

# Test experiments

## Base

    ./run-test-base.sh
    mv logs logs-test-base
    ./summarize-test.sh logs-test-base/*

## Tuned

    ./run-test.sh
    mv logs logs-test-tuned
    ./summarize-test.sh logs-test-tuned/*
